content:
Submit Time Off with Resource Absences

Workforce Engagement is available in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

Shift Scheduling is available in the Contact Center Stock Keeping Unit (SKU), Einstein 1 Service Edition, and Service Suites.

To submit a resource absence: 

You need to be a Shift Scheduling Planner or Workforce Engagement Planner.

Open Service Resources in the App Launcher.
Click on your Service Resource record.
Click Related.
Scroll down to Absences, and click New.
Fill in the details of your absence.
Save your changes.
title: Service Cloud Time Off Management
